Patrol Cop (Node js)
--------------------

To run this app simply install the following in order (on a Terminal (ubuntu))
 "node js"
 "npm"

install the following dependencies using npm 
 "body-parser" npm install body-parser
 "crypto-js"
 "express" 

to start the app run
node index.js

controlls:
use keyboard arrows to drive around.
use key 'L' to locate or get the cop car current coordinates
